60.7	Charlie_Kaufman	Charlie Kaufman	Charles Stuart "Charlie" Kaufman (born November 19, 1958) is an American screenwriter, producer, and director. His film work includes Being John Malkovich, Human Nature, Adaptation, Eternal Sunshine of the Spotless Mind and Synecdoche, New York. He won the Academy Award for Best Original Screenplay for Eternal Sunshine of the Spotless Mind.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/5d/Charliekaufman.JPG/240px-Charliekaufman.JPG
